{"tid":2058002,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"85歲達賴喇嘛首度推出音樂專輯","createTime":"2020-06-09T23:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T17:14:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"02d8d65d55ccb98074fa7a4c050c1c153ccf2968","tid":2058002,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:22:07.000Z","msg":"（中央社紐約9日綜合外電報導）紐西蘭音樂家簡妮拉顧寧一心希望製作達賴喇嘛誦經的音樂專輯，最後終獲這位西藏精神領袖同意，經過5年努力，這個專輯「內在世界」即將於7月6日達賴喇嘛85歲生日當天發行。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，「內在世界」專輯（Inner World，暫譯）共有11個曲目，內容是達賴喇嘛唱誦經文，主題包括智慧、勇氣、療癒和兒童等。發行時並將附有一本小冊子。<br />\n<br />\n身為佛教徒的簡妮拉顧寧（Junelle Kunin）原先在銀行工作時，因壓力過大，開始找尋搭配達賴喇嘛講經的音樂，希望有助獲得平靜，結果在網路上遍尋不得。她於是向達賴喇嘛的辦公室建議，合作製作他誦經的音樂專輯，結果對方委婉拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/84Fe-2ezVsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F84Fe-2ezVsc&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a65c6141\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/84Fe-2ezVsc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QmMVXf7Jwog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQmMVXf7Jwog&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a167d161\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QmMVXf7Jwog</a><br />\n<br />\n影片來源：Dalai Lama - Inner World<br />\n她後來趁2015年造訪印度拜見達賴喇嘛時再度提起此事，並列出專輯涵蓋的主題與經文，這次終於獲得回音。經過5年努力，「內在世界」順利誕生。<br />\n<br />\n簡妮拉顧寧說，達賴喇嘛當時談起此事時頗為興奮，並向她解釋音樂為何重要。她說：「他的眼睛閃閃發亮&hellip;他談起音樂如何能夠幫助大眾，為他所不能，因為它可以超脫歧見，讓我們回歸自性和善心。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：林治平）1090609<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006100004.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202006100004.aspx&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=47b8fe90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202006100004.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"cb172f50c5c43479fcd7601d83f187d0edf3b1c9","tid":2058002,"uid":54486,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:23:18.000Z","msg":"真。活佛viva"},{"pid":"a24a0ce2ddb9a126b6a7d2d293d832cb53a2e422","tid":2058002,"uid":205684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:36:47.000Z","msg":"訓覺前聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ccdab37a11e557bd5becde264e92134dfe9e73","tid":2058002,"uid":203251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:37:38.000Z","msg":"召喚Vini Vici psytrance remix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFree Tibet"},{"pid":"cd0566b2f4f0a3bcf20970d42fd94fd64be7d5c9","tid":2058002,"uid":154176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:37:52.000Z","msg":"Smoke住聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2834dccfebac6d2f0e6493139cbcc2a92e9d86","tid":2058002,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:39:43.000Z","msg":"我佛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093ee4efbe851cdf6c0d081df1c6450d7e813444","tid":2058002,"uid":99700,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:45:40.000Z","msg":"DLLM 專輯"},{"pid":"25689db6e117e944bc38bc1a12199ae90d5e3860","tid":2058002,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:47:29.000Z","msg":"係咩令到佢五年內改變主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8472f11552d8307150cf774ff42f6a3cb30014b","tid":2058002,"uid":107681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:47:43.000Z","msg":"年輕得剃度誰亦能像波惹般乾脆<br />\n快活到半日也像活佛一百萬歲<br />\n任何事亦能像釋迦般清脆<br />\n快活到每日大一歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fe3ce77733f937061b344427d2ef7b3c300971","tid":2058002,"uid":83328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T23:47:54.000Z",